  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    British Embassy Chisinau call for proposals: State Forestry Agency Reform
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This call for proposals specifically seeks applications for projects related to the reform of the State Forestry Agency, “Moldsilva”. </p>

  </div>
